AspireLdap bundled OpenLDAP container sources
==============================================

The Dockerfile and shell scripts in this directory (openldap/) are derived from
the Bitnami OpenLDAP container:

    https://github.com/bitnami/containers/tree/main/bitnami/openldap
    Copyright Broadcom, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

They were rewritten for this project to install OpenLDAP from stock Debian
packages instead of Bitnami-distributed binaries, but remain a derivative work
and are distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see the LICENSE file
in this directory).

